The paper discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for securing IIoT systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the challenges and real-world considerations associated with this matter, which could fall under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the integration of machine learning into the security mechanisms of IIoT systems, which could fall under the category of software engineering (cs.SE).
